          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2015-06-24T20:14:03Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Equal Justice for Our Military Act of 2015</strong></p> <p>Amends the federal judicial code to allow for review by writ of certiorari of certain cases denied relief or review by the U.S. Court of Appeals for the Armed Forces.</p> <p>Declares that the time for application for such a writ shall be as prescribed by rules of the Supreme Court.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2015-06-18T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
